er enables single-scattering albedos and scattering\nasymmetry factors to be retrieved from James Webb Space Telescope phase curves\nof exoplanets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jan 2021 09:58:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Feb 2021 20:08:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 9 Mar 2021 08:48:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-17"}
